{
    "schema_version":  "histoweave.domain_mappings.v1",
    "description":  "Cross-platform cell_type -\u003e domain collapse tables. Each map takes a platform-specific cell_type / cluster label and collapses it into a small set of tissue-level compartments so ARI can be computed against \u0027domain_truth\u0027. User-selected Q6: \u0027domain-prior collapse\u0027 semantic.",
